        "hash": "34344c3626e5f02b8ed03fb74245a6ea408f29c2",
        "author": "Sumit",
        "msg": "feat: tree-sitter ingestion, HelixDB writes, semantic pass, viz dump\n\n- scalable_ingest.py: replaced ast with tree-sitter; extracts CONTAINS,\n  IMPORTS, INHERITS, CALLS edges; writes all nodes/edges live to HelixDB\n  (localhost:6969) via helix-db SDK; keeps graph_payload.json + graph_viz.json\n  as artefacts\n\n- semantic_pass.py: separate post-ingestion pass; traverses Commit->GENERATED->\n  FunctionState in HelixDB; analyses code structurally (params, calls, branches,\n  returns) to derive per-function Concept nodes and a ChangeNode summary;\n  attaches Rationale from commit message body; guardrail prevents writing\n  AST-owned node kinds\n\n- dump_viz.py: merges graph_payload.json with semantic nodes from HelixDB into\n  graph_viz.json for tools/harness_graph_viz.html\n\n- tools/harness_graph_viz.html: force-directed graph explorer (load JSON)",
        "timestamp": "2026-06-24T22:56:02+05:45",
        "ai_rationale": ""
      }
    },
